APB-DynaSonics

The future of pro audio is one of quality and convenience.

Digital and analog technologies each have their place in the development of mixing consoles. Quality should never be compromised for convenience. Space, depth and the emotion of a live performance must be reproduced at its original resolution. The audienceâ€™s emotional connection with the artist is everything.
